                    <h2>Thrive on Long Island, venture into the city</h2>
                    <p>Situated on Long Island, New York, you'll feel safe and settled in a beautiful campus and supportive campus. The famed Hmptons and beaches surround the university, giving you a breath of fresh air and peaceful escape.
Ready to experience what lies beyond? New York City is just 40 km and a short train ride from campus. Soak in the city life, unlimited cultural experiences and restaurants featuring every world vuisine. Named the #1 Most Influential City in the World (Business Insider 2018), you'll find much more than entertainment in the NYC. You'll find promising career opportunities, such as an internship with the United Nations or a Fortune 500 company in the industry of your choice. New York is home to the most Fortune 500 companies in the country, so you'll be sure to find career opportunities tailored to your interests.</p>

                </div>
