            <section class="l-page-block l-text-block">
                <div class="l-content-container">
                    <h2>Add cutting-edge technology to your education</h2>
                    <p>Hofstra understands the importance of real experience for the real world. All of its programs are backed by state-of-the-art facilities that enhance your learning. Whether you'e studying in class, participating in a student organization or researching for a project with practical implications, Hofstra University provides you with the right resources.</p>
<p>Imagine learning about investing in one of the largest academic trading rooms in the nation. Learn to trade stocks, invest in companies, and build a business plan in the 52,000 square-foot Frank Z. Garb School of Business. The building opened its doors in January 2019 and also features the Behavioral Science and Market Research Lab where you can research consumers’ physical and physiological behavior with the latest technology to analyze their engagement process to a brand or a product.</p>
<p>One of only nine US universities to collaborate in a cybersecurity program with Facebook, you can participate in the cybersecurity training coding academy with Facebook and CodePath.org for free. If engineering and science are in your future, explore the innovative Fred DeMatteis School of Engineering and Applied Science or School of Natural Sciences and Mathematics. The Lawrence Herbert School of communication boasts impressive programs for broadcasting, filming, and writing. Get real-world experience working alongside accomplished faculty before you even graduate.</p>

